#: Game.Levels.SubsetWorld.L07_NonSubset
msgid "# When âٹ† Fails: Proving آ¬(s âٹ† t)\n"
"\n"
"All the subset proofs so far have been **positive**: you showed that\n"
"one set is contained in another. But what if the containment is\n"
"**false**? How do you prove آ§0?\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, آ§1 is defined as آ§2. So to prove آ§3,\n"
"you use آ§4 to **assume** the subset holds, getting\n"
"آ§5, and then derive a contradiction (آ§6).\n"
"\n"
"To derive the contradiction, exhibit a **counterexample**: find an\n"
"element that is in آ§7 but not in آ§8. If the subset held, this\n"
"element would have to be in both â€” but it is not, so we get آ§9.\n"
"\n"
"In Level 1, we noted that آ§10 is false\n"
"because 4 is in the first set but not the second. Now you will prove\n"
"this formally.\n"
"\n"
"**Proof plan**:\n"
"1. آ§11 â€” assume the subset holds (goal becomes آ§12)\n"
"2. Prove آ§13 â€” show the witness is in the domain\n"
"3. Apply آ§14 to get آ§15 â€” use the assumed subset\n"
"4. Unwrap and derive contradiction â€” آ§16 is false"
msgstr ""

