#: Game.Levels.SubsetWorld.L14_ProperSubset
msgid "# Strict Containment: The Proper Subset âٹ‚\n"
"\n"
"You have proved all three partial order axioms for آ§0 (reflexivity,\n"
"transitivity, antisymmetry). Antisymmetry says: if آ§1 and\n"
"آ§2, then آ§3. In other words, mutual containment forces\n"
"equality.\n"
"\n"
"But what about **strict** containment â€” when one set is inside\n"
"another but they are NOT equal? This is the **proper subset**\n"
"relation, written آ§4.\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, آ§5 means آ§6 â€” آ§7 is contained in\n"
"آ§8, and the containment is strict (there is something in آ§9 that is\n"
"not in آ§10).\n"
"\n"
"To prove آ§11, use آ§12 to split into two goals:\n"
"1. Prove آ§13 â€” a familiar subset proof\n"
"2. Prove آ§14 â€” a familiar non-subset proof (Level 7)\n"
"\n"
"This level integrates two skills you have already mastered!\n"
"\n"
"**Proof plan**:\n"
"1. آ§15 â€” split آ§16 into آ§17 and آ§18\n"
"2. **First goal** (آ§19): prove the subset as in Level 1\n"
"3. **Second goal** (آ§20): disprove the reverse as in Level 7"
msgstr ""

